<H1>Pipes Digest Article Search</H1>
This is a case-insensitive substring search: thus
searching for 'ian' will find 'Ian' and Adriana'.
The search is for all of the keywords appearing in one
digest article.
Up to the first 100 matches are returned.
The search engine is
<a href="http://glimpse.cs.arizona.edu/">glimpse</a>
and a script written by me.
