<H3>Health for all database</H3>

<a href="../www.who.dk/mainframe.htm"><H4>Online version of HFA database</H4></A>

The HFA database is available under both DOS and Windows. The Windows version can be used with Windows 3.1 and 3.11 or Windows 95.

<H4><UL>
<LI><a href="dosexpl.htm">Instructions for DOS installation</A>
<LI><a href="winexp.htm">Instructions for Windows installation</A>
<LI><a href="sethfaw.exe">Download the database for Windows</A>
<li><a href="sethfad.exe">Download the database for MS/DOS</A>
</UL></H4>



