<center>
<h1>Environment and Health</h1>

<HR>
</center>
The Environment and Health Department helps countries to  tackle the long-term prevention of environmental hazards to health, including the pollution of air, water and soil, as well as environmental emergencies and accidents. It promotes food safety, occupational health and healthy housing.
<p>
<h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="tpeh01.htm">Policy statements</A>
<li><a href="tpeh02.htm">Programmes</A>
<li><a href="./eh/airqual.htm">Air quality</A>
<li><a href="tpeh03.htm">Documentation</A>
</ul>
</h4>





<hr>
