<H1>Press notes 2</H1>


updated 12.9.96

<H3>WHO Regional Office for Europe<BR>
Communication and Public Affairs<BR>
Scherfigsvej 8<BR>
2100 Copenhagen<BR>
Denmark</H3>

<B>Tel. (45) 39 17 13 44 and 39 17 13 36<BR>
Fax. (45) 39 17 18 80<BR>
</B>
<H3>Press notes</H3>


summarize recent and upcoming newsworthy WHO activities, products
and services.  For each entry, a contact person is identified
for more details and technical information. The Communication
and Public Affairs (CPA) Unit is ready to help you with your coverage
of these subjects by providing graphics, pictures, video material
(where available) and by identifying regional and national experts
