<title>Introduction</title>
<body background="../cbcbg01.gif">

<img src="bookhead.gif">
<br>
<a href="../Welcome.htm"><img src="../homeknap.gif"></A>
<a href="publicat.htm"><img src="../sectknap.gif"></A>
<a href="prelim.htm"><img src="../prevknap.gif"></A>
<a href="aids.htm"><img src="../nextknap.gif"></A>



<H1 align=middle> Introduction</H1>
<HR>
This catalogue provides, <B>in the first section,</B> bibliographic and descriptive information for books published by the
WHO Regional Office for Europe from 1990 to 1996.  The <B>second section</B> gives similar information on books
published on behalf of the Regional Office in the same period.  The catalogue also includes a limited selection of
older titles.<P>

<H2>Organization</H2>
The catalogue of Regional Office books is organized according to the subject headings listed in the table of contents.
Within each subject category, books are listed chronologically.<P>
The books published on behalf of the Regional Office are arranged alphabetically by publisher.<P>


<H2>Languages</H2>
The following abbreviations are used to indicate the availability of different language editions: E = English; F =
French; G = German; R = Russian.  An asterisk (*) denotes a language edition in preparation.<P>
<HR>

<H2>How to order Regional Office books</H2>
Orders may be addressed to any of the <A HREF="sales.htm">sales agents </A>or directly to: <br>World Health
Organization,<br> Distribution and Sales,<br>
 1211 Geneva 27,<BR>
 Switzerland. <br>
E-mail to <a href=mailto:Publications@who.ch>Publications@who.ch</A><p>
Please note that all orders addressed to WHO
headquarters in Geneva must be accompanied by payment in Swiss francs, US dollars or Unesco coupons.  Credit
cards are also accepted.<P>
<H3>Please note that orders should not be addressed to the
Regional Office in Copenhagen.</H3>
<HR>
<H2>How to order books published on behalf of the
Regional Office</H2>
Orders for these books should be placed through a bookseller.  They are not available
through WHO.<P>
<hr>
<center>
<table>
<tr><td><img src="../whoblk.gif"></td><td>   WHO Regional Office for Europe<BR>
<font size=2>URL: http://www.who.dk/</font><BR>
<font size=2><i>Updated 25 November 1996 - jfr@who.dk</i></font></td></tr>
</table>

