<H3>Unemployment, social vulnerability, and health in
Europe</H3>

Edited by D. Schwefel, P.-G. Svensson and H. Zllner<P>

1987, 325 pages<BR>
ISBN 3 540 17867 8<BR>
DM 148.-<P>

