<a href<a href="resolu.htm"><img src="../nextknap.gif"></A>



<H1 align=center>Regional Committee for Europe</H1>

<hr>
Representatives of each <a href="../country/members.htm"><b>Member State</b></A> in the European Region makes up the WHO Regional Committee for Europe. It meets every year in September for five days. At these meetings the Member States formulate regional policies, recommend and supervise WHO/Europe's activities and approve the budget. Their decisions take the form of <a href="resolu.htm"><b>resolutions</b></a> that are the basis for further work in the European Region.

<P>
<hr>
<center>
