<H2>Election of Members of the Standing Committee of the
Regional Committee</H2>

<UL>
<LI>The Regional Committee,
<LI>Having considered document EUR/RC45/13 giving details of the candidates proposed for election to
the Standing Committee of the Regional Committee;
</UL>
